  "title": "Campaign Sales Representative",
  "description": "<p>🚨 Fresh Graduates, Newly ORD, and Career Changers — Ready to Kickstart Your Career?<br>\nYour next big opportunity is here, combining growth, excitement, and unlimited earning potential.</p>\n<p>No experience? Don’t worry.<br>\nWe’ll provide full training, step-by-step guidance, and mentorship to help you become a confident and effective sales consultant.</p>\n<h2>⚡ What You’ll Be Doing</h2>\n<ul>\n  <li>Attend high-energy events and roadshows</li>\n  <li>Participate in B2B campaigns to strengthen professional communication</li>\n  <li>Engage directly with clients to build trust and confidence</li>\n  <li>Work alongside a motivated and supportive team</li>\n  <li>Attend workshops that improve your sales, leadership, and interpersonal skills</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>💰 What You’ll Gain</h2>\n<ul>\n  <li>Weekly payouts with uncapped commissions</li>\n  <li>Performance bonuses for achievers</li>\n  <li>Leadership tracks for fast movers</li>\n  <li>Travel opportunities for exposure</li>\n  <li>Supportive team culture that celebrates your growth</li>\n  <li>Open to Singaporeans/PRs aged 18+</li>\n</ul>\n<p>🚀 If you’re motivated, ambitious, and ready to grow fast, don’t wait — apply today!</p>",
